long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: As all we know, unfortunately Clickup doesn't support RTL by default. It means you will have plenty of problems in Arabic, Hebrew, Persian, Urdu, Kashmiri, Pashto, Uighur, Sorani Kurdish, and Sindhi languages. With "Clickup RTL!" you can view the Clickup app in RTL mode with a better font. Affects task's inner view, forms, notifications section, etc.
